     • z.<span style='font-family:"Arial",sans-serif'>&#8239;</span>B. vors<span
     style='mso-ascii-font-family:Aptos;mso-hansi-font-family:Aptos;mso-bidi-font-family:
     Aptos'>ä</span>tzlicher Mord<br>
     <span style='mso-ascii-font-family:Aptos;mso-hansi-font-family:Aptos;
     mso-bidi-font-family:Aptos'>•</span> selbst glaubw<span style='mso-ascii-font-family:
